            <title>[LU-10182] &quot;MDT name too long&quot; inaccurate</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10182</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in liblustreapi.c if a MDT name of &quot;fsname-MDT000&quot; is specified, you get &quot;error: MDT name too long |fsname-MDT000|&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Changing the message to &quot;Invalid MDT name&quot; would solve the problem, without changing the logic.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
